001232  1               ;------------------------------------------------------------------
001232  1               ; game_over_loop — blink "SPACE = PLAY AGAIN"; wait for input
001232  1               ;------------------------------------------------------------------
001232  1               game_over_loop:
001232  1  20 3F 09        jsr wait_vsync
001235  1  E6 rr           inc frame_count
001237  1  20 41 09        jsr update_input
00123A  1               
