001376  1               
001376  1               ;------------------------------------------------------------------
001376  1               ; wave_clear_loop — wait for SPACE or timer expiry
001376  1               ;------------------------------------------------------------------
001376  1               wave_clear_loop:
001376  1  20 3F 09        jsr wait_vsync
001379  1  20 41 09        jsr update_input
00137C  1               
